data.description: Seller offering a Buyer Credit of $7,500 with an accepted offer!! Nestled in highly sought-after northwest Boise, this 3-bedroom home offers the perfect blend of tranquility & convenience with breathtaking views of the foothills right from your backyard. Embrace the spacious open concept floorplan, perfect for entertaining friends & family. The seamless flow between the living, dining, & kitchen areas creates an inviting space for gatherings & relaxation. The primary bedroom comes complete with a private bathroom, offering a tranquil retreat within your own home. A new roof installed in 2021 ensures worry-free living, while new lighting & plumbing fixtures add a touch of elegance to every room. The newer laminate floors brings a modern touch, combining style & durability. Experience the beauty of mature shade trees & no rear neighbors providing added privacy, allowing you to enjoy the serene outdoors in peace. Benefit from quick easy access to foothills trails, Boise River Greenbelt.
